[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.091,
    "text": "Think she's cheatin' on me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.092,
    "endTime": 2.4850000000000003,
    "text": "No, I don't think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.485,
    "endTime": 4.388,
    "text": "Well you should definitely talk to her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.389,
    "endTime": 8.035,
    "text": "She's cheatin' on ya bro—drop her, right? [The Perks of Being Straightforward.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.035,
    "endTime": 8.943,
    "text": "[The Perks of Being Straightforward.]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.359,
    "endTime": 10.617,
    "text": "Nice tights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.494,
    "endTime": 13.096,
    "text": "Are you flirting with me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.096,
    "endTime": 14.506,
    "text": "Maybe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.506,
    "endTime": 16.944,
    "text": "You wanna take me out tonight, you should just ask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.944,
    "endTime": 18.413,
    "text": "Wha... damn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.413,
    "endTime": 22.268,
    "text": "Personally, I love being one of the many girls who is blunt and honest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.268,
    "endTime": 24.457,
    "text": "I mean, it gets you what you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.689,
    "endTime": 29.63,
    "text": "Also, we're usually the ones who decide where the group of friends is gonna eat for lunch that day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.63,
    "endTime": 30.766,
    "text": "We should get sushi today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.766,
    "endTime": 31.834,
    "text": "No, no, no, let's get Chinese food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.834,
    "endTime": 33.255,
    "text": "Okay, but sushi's better so..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.255,
    "endTime": 34.591,
    "text": "No, Chinese food sounds good right now so..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.591,
    "endTime": 35.759,
    "text": "Okay, it's the same thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.759,
    "endTime": 36.873,
    "text": "No, that's racist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.873,
    "endTime": 39.009,
    "text": "Uh, stop it—we are getting Mexican."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.009,
    "endTime": 40.472,
    "text": "So that's cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.472,
    "endTime": 42.956,
    "text": "But sometimes, you can rub people the wrong way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.956,
    "endTime": 44.256,
    "text": "(Chuckling)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.256,
    "endTime": 46.207,
    "text": "Chris, you gotta take that hat off man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.207,
    "endTime": 48.877,
    "text": "New Years was like two weeks ago, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.877,
    "endTime": 51.150000000000006,
    "text": "My dead grandmother gave me this hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.694,
    "endTime": 55.956,
    "text": "And uh, sometimes, it can get you into trouble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.956,
    "endTime": 58.118,
    "text": "Guys, we just had a crazy year this year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.118,
    "endTime": 59.325,
    "text": "Yeah, like that tie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.325,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.815,
    "endTime": 64.851,
    "text": "But people trust us for the truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.851,
    "endTime": 66.454,
    "text": "And those are my ideas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.454,
    "endTime": 68.27099999999999,
    "text": "(clapping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.272,
    "endTime": 69.203,
    "text": "-Great. -Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.203,
    "endTime": 70.961,
    "text": "-Really good job. -Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.961,
    "endTime": 72.06,
    "text": "-Quinta. -Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.06,
    "endTime": 72.848,
    "text": "How was it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.848,
    "endTime": 73.884,
    "text": "Girl, you killed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.884,
    "endTime": 74.606,
    "text": "-Really? -Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.606,
    "endTime": 75.289,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.289,
    "endTime": 80.012,
    "text": "And when we do get what we want, we usually have a ball with people who appreciate us the way we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.013,
    "endTime": 80.664,
    "text": "You're gonna come over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.664,
    "endTime": 81.231,
    "text": "Mmmhmm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.231,
    "endTime": 83.19,
    "text": "And you're gonna meet my friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.19,
    "endTime": 84.908,
    "text": "Don't tell me what I'm gonna do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.616,
    "endTime": 86.515,
    "text": "Well, it's not a big deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.515,
    "endTime": 88.396,
    "text": "You're gonna come over and you're gonna meet my friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.149,
    "endTime": 90.299,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.299,
    "endTime": 93.295,
    "text": "And we're the kind of people who can start a revolution."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.295,
    "endTime": 96.429,
    "text": "I can't give you guys Martin Luther King Day off this year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.429,
    "endTime": 97.474,
    "text": "(slapping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.474,
    "endTime": 99.355,
    "text": "That is unacceptable, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.355,
    "endTime": 103.88300000000001,
    "text": "Martin Luther King did not die for our sins, so that we could work on his birthday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.883,
    "endTime": 104.926,
    "text": "I thought that was Jesus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.927,
    "endTime": 106.739,
    "text": "I don't know. I just want the day off, so let's hear it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.739,
    "endTime": 107.458,
    "text": "Amen to that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.458,
    "endTime": 108.596,
    "text": "(clapping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.596,
    "endTime": 109.78,
    "text": "(cheering) We should not work on that day!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.179,
    "endTime": 113.263,
    "text": "Okay...okay. You guys have the day off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.263,
    "endTime": 115.492,
    "text": "Basically, keep being blunt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.492,
    "endTime": 117.396,
    "text": "The world needs people like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.396,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Otherwise, how would we get anything done?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.202,
    "text": "Alright guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.202,
    "endTime": 123.828,
    "text": "I think we should still get Chinese food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.828,
    "endTime": 128.30700000000002,
    "text": "Eugene Lee Yang, we are getting Mexican food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.541,
    "endTime": 130.305,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.306,
    "endTime": 130.965,
    "text": "Come, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.965,
    "endTime": 132.423,
    "text": "Okay."
